dmca.title: DMCA (Copyright) Complaint to Google
dmca.sender_name: Greek American Heritage Society of Philadelphia

works.description:
The logo mark on the homepage is the same
 
as the one used at our legitimate site, www.gahsp.org. The Owl used as a  

symbol of wisdom is the primary copyrighted piece.

The site also attempts to collect donations under the guise that they will
 
go to the Greek American Heritage Society of Philadelphia. The PayPal  
accounts are not the same.

This site was constructed by a previous subcontractor, Paul Kotrosios, who
 
is refusing to take it down. We have contacted him by phone and tried to  

resolve this amicably but have not been successful.
